                    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-sm text-yellow-900 space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Page not found (404)?</strong> Verify @@page directive is on the first line and the
                            route matches your URL.</li>
                        <li><strong>@@ symbol shows as literal text?</strong> You're inside a Razor comment or HTML. Use
                            @@ directly in C# context.</li>
                        <li><strong>Format string error?</strong> Check for typos in format strings - they're
                            case-sensitive ("MM" ‚â† "mm").</li>
                        <li><strong>Time doesn't update?</strong> Blazor Server only updates when page refreshes. For
                            real-time updates, you need a timer with StateHasChanged().</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
